biography: Ariana Greenblatt is an American actress who has transitioned from Disney Channel star to Hollywood talent. Greenblatt's breakout role was in the Disney Channel series Stuck in the Middle from 2016–2018. She has also appeared in the films Avengers: Infinity War (2018), A Bad Moms Christmas, Barbie (2023), and the upcoming Now You See Me installment.
name: Ariana Greenblatt
